<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    .order-details {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .item {
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 10px;
      background: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .changes {
      background: #fff3cd;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Your Order #{{orderId}} Has Been Modified and Confirmed</h2>
  <p>Dear {{firstName}},</p>
  <p>Your order has been modified and confirmed. Below are the updated details of your order:</p>

  <div class="changes">
    <h4>Changes Made to Your Order:</h4>
    {{#each changes}}
      <p>{{this}}</p>
    {{/each}}
  </div>

  <div class="order-details">
    <h3>Updated Order Details:</h3>
    <p><strong>Total Amount:</strong> {{totalAmount}} CHF</p>
    
    <h4>Items:</h4>
    {{#each items}}
      <div class="item">
        <p><strong>{{product.name}}</strong></p>
        <p>Quantity: {{quantity}}</p>
        <p>Price: {{price}} CHF</p>
      </div>
    {{/each}}

    <h4>Delivery Information:</h4>
    <p><strong>Delivery Method:</strong> {{deliveryDetails.type}}</p>
    <p>{{deliveryDetails.details}}</p>
  </div>

  <p>If you have any questions about these changes, please contact us.</p>
  <p>Thank you for your understanding!</p>
</body>
</html>